message.body: Happy birthday #! I hope you are celebrating in a suitably ### fashion.
Thanks! I am, although in the less popular "dark room and whiskey from the bottle" fashion. That one hasn't gotten a lot of rotation lately, so I thought us bust it out for old time's sake
Sometimes it's not a bad way to go. So long as it's in the rock and roll fashion and not the crushing depression fashion
Try to turn it into the rock and roll version. :)
